OL,3,CCost saving measures needed to plug
OL,4,CGuernsey's #100m shortfall
OL,6,FA Guernsey business leader has warned
OL,7,Fcandidates for the island's election
OL,8,Fnext year to seriously consider cost-
OL,9,Fsaving measures to fund an eye-
OL,10,Fwatering #650 million in committed
OL,11,Fspending.
OL,13,FIt comes as the States of Guernsey
OL,14,Fagreed to pave the way for a Goods and
OL,15,FServices Tax, after four days of
OL,16,Fdebate.
