OL,3,CCost saving measures needed to plug
OL,4,CGuernsey's #100m shortfall
OL,6,FFrom 2027, people in Guernsey will be
OL,7,Fpaying an extra five per cent on
OL,8,Falmost everything they buy, with
OL,9,Fproposals to raise income tax by 10%
OL,10,Fbeing defeated.
OL,12,FWhile the States has committed to
OL,13,Fintroducing GST, it's likely to take
OL,14,Ftwo years and cost up to #3 million to
OL,15,Fset up.
OL,17,FPoliticians believe the GST Plus
OL,18,Fpackage will raise #50 million a year.
