OL,3,CCost saving measures needed to plug
OL,4,CGuernsey's #100m shortfall
OL,6,FHowever, there are concerns about how
OL,7,Fthe States will fund their agreed #650
OL,8,Fmillion worth of spending.
OL,10,FWith an upcoming election next June,
OL,11,FPresident of Guernsey Chamber of
OL,12,FCommerce, Stephen Rouxel, says that
OL,13,Fcandidates must consider how they can
OL,14,Fhandle the States' ballooning
OL,15,Fshortfall and spending.
OL,17,FHe explains: "If you're going to stand
OL,18,Fon a 'No to GST' ticket, you need to
OL,19,Freally understand what is a credible
OL,20,Foption.
