OL,3,CCost saving measures needed to plug
OL,4,CGuernsey's #100m shortfall
OL,6,F"What costs are you going to cut? Are
OL,7,Fyou getting rid of cancer care? Are
OL,8,Fyou getting rid of NICE drugs?
OL,10,F"Someone in the last election (said)
OL,11,F"I'd cut the Police Force by 25%"
OL,12,F(but) that saves you #200,000 and we
OL,13,Fneed #70 million. So don't come with
OL,14,Fideas for cost savings unless you
OL,15,Freally know what that means."
OL,17,FThe Committee for Policy and Resources
OL,18,Fwill consider its next steps at a
OL,19,Fmeeting on Tuesday 12 November in what
OL,20,Fcould become an emergency budget, if
OL,21,Fapproved by Deputies.
